# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:15
translate chinese danap7_8bb004fc:

    # cw "A little."
    cw "有一点。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:17
translate chinese danap7_65cff493:

    # cw "I don't think he would do anything, but I didn't think he would ever hit me either."
    cw "我不认为他会做什么，但我以前也没想过他会打我。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:18
translate chinese danap7_795ff652:

    # cw "He's obviously more violent than I thought he was."
    cw "他显然比我想象的更暴力。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:20
translate chinese danap7_5b958a41:

    # cw "So yeah, there's this little fear in the back of my mind that he'll come after me again."
    cw "所以，我心里确实隐隐担心他会再找我麻烦。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:21
translate chinese danap7_8886e106:

    # cw "Or that he'll call work and tell Mrs. Mills about our relationship and she'll fire me over it."
    cw "或者他会给公司打电话，把我们的关系告诉米尔斯夫人，然后她会因此解雇我。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:22
translate chinese danap7_5ec84979:

    # cw "I have rent to pay now. I really can't lose my job."
    cw "我现在得交房租。真的不能丢了这份工作。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:24
translate chinese danap7_b6160319:

    # pc "I don't think she'd fire you."
    pc "我觉得她不会解雇你的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:25
translate chinese danap7_3a09722d:

    # pc "You do too much work there. She'd fire me first. Or I'd just quit."
    pc "你在那儿干得那么勤快。她肯定先解雇我。或者我干脆自己辞职。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:26
translate chinese danap7_607dcdf8:

    # pc "I wouldn't want you to lose your job over me."
    pc "我可不希望你因为我丢了工作。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:28
translate chinese danap7_c29d12da:

    # cw "Like I said, he probably wouldn't do anything."
    cw "就像我说的，他大概不会做什么的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:30
translate chinese danap7_c5b5ed91:

    # cw "Liz says that I should see a therapist."
    cw "莉兹说我应该去看心理医生。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:31
translate chinese danap7_e8c6ff85:

    # pc "You probably should. You've been through some trauma."
    pc "你确实应该去。你经历过一些创伤。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:33
translate chinese danap7_b879ed1d:

    # cw "Yeah, I guess I have."
    cw "是啊，我想确实如此。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:35
translate chinese danap7_4ddb3132:

    # cw "I'll call somebody tomorrow."
    cw "我明天就联系看看。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:36
translate chinese danap7_f07574ec:

    # pc "Good."
    pc "好。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:38
translate chinese danap7_694841ff:

    # cw "What if you just stayed with me all the time, to protect me?"
    cw "要不你一直待在我身边，保护我？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:39
translate chinese danap7_33a308fe:

    # pc "I'll always do everything I can to protect you..."
    pc "我会尽我所能保护你……"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:40
translate chinese danap7_e7379772:

    # cw "But you can't be around all the time. I know."
    cw "但你不可能一直陪着我。我知道。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:42
translate chinese danap7_8d255b1f:

    # cw "And you shouldn't have to be."
    cw "而且你也不该非得这样。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:43
translate chinese danap7_179c195e:

    # cw "I shouldn't be scared to be alone."
    cw "我不该害怕一个人。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:44
translate chinese danap7_28cd97a2:

    # cw "I'll work on it."
    cw "我会努力的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:45
translate chinese danap7_bc5db1db:

    # pc "I love you Dana. I just want you to be happy."
    pc "我爱你，达娜。我只想让你幸福。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danap7.rpy:47
translate chinese danap7_1097f75f:

    # cw "I know. I love you too."
    cw "我知道。我也爱你。"

